{"data":[{"date":"09:02 09/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Torreira t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m 2013, Lucas Torreira r\u1eddi qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Pescara. Ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie B, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Sampdoria v\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi 1,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Torreira ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho Pescara d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u00f9a 2015/16, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng tri\u1ec7u h\u1ed3i anh v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 2 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, Torreira \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i 35 tr\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u00ean t\u1ea1i Serie A cho Sampdoria. \u1ede m\u00f9a 2017/18, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00e1t ti\u1ebft m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng (ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68) song Torreira c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Torreira-sap-toi-Arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Torreira ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Sampdoria</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Torreira n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh nh\u01b0 c\u1eaft. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Uruguay c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t hay s\u00fat xa\u2026 T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Serie A hay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Arsenal v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 Torreira \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1o li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Sampdoria \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua anh. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 26,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Torreira\" title=\"tien ve Torreira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111i k\u00e8m Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Anh c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Uruguay c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Torreira n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Telenoche. \u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed n\u00f3.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Arsenal, Torreira s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng Stephan Lichtsteiner, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV m\u1edbi Unai Emery thay Arsene Wenger.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-27-trieu-bang-mua-cristian-pavon-172-190516.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Cristian Pavon</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-vu-sao-khung-argentina-421-190433.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\">Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1065","checkdouble":"190746"},{"date":"10:02 09/07","title":"Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0a tin, Arsenal \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Matteo Guendouzi.</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Matteo Guendouzi\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal</span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Lorient \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Matteo Guendouzi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. Anh l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PSG nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Lorient n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd RMC Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u00e0 Guendouzi s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi London trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates. Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB Lorient c\u1ee7a Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng kh\u1ecfi Ligue 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tranh su\u1ea5t th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Guendouzi c\u00f3 21 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Guendouzi r\u1eddi Lorient \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Lorient. Anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Do v\u1eady, ra \u0111i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Guendouzi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ea7n Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 khi Torreira c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay \u1edf World Cup 2018. Theo nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Torreira, anh s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m London Colney trong h\u00f4m nay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-172-190746.html\">Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1064","checkdouble":"190748"},{"date":"09:27 09/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed5i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng U19 \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/doi-gio-thi-dau-u19-viet-nam-con-co-hoi-vuot-qua-vong-bang-u19-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Elneny t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 khi Arsenal b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.</h2><h2>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo. Anh kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi West Ham h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Elneny \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Pharaoh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m do \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/elneny-hao-huc-truoc-mua-giai-201819-cung-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Emirates, Elneny \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi HLV Wenger ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Elneny v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p Boreham Wood v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5. HLV Unai Emery b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno, trung\u00a0 v\u1ec7 Sokratis, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 3 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn London ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi-172-190748.html\">Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1063","checkdouble":"190749"},{"date":"09:46 09/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/cong-phuong-len-tieng-sau-tinh-huong-mat-kiem-che-voi-thu-mon-tuan-manh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee9a thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau pha&nbsp;n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-2, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0nh vi n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi qua ti\u1ebfng l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, bu\u1ed9c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cong phuong\" title=\"c\u00f4ng ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/cong-phuong-len-tieng-sau-tinh-huong-mat-kiem-che-voi-thu-mon-tuan-manh.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e2u gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. \u1ea2nh: Sport5.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Th\u00f4ng qua trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Anh n\u00f3i: &quot;H\u00f4m nay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng mong l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng tin v\u00e0 hi v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng m\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. H\u00f4m nay, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 &ldquo;bu\u1ed3n&rdquo; c\u00f2n bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec c\u00e1i g\u00ec ch\u1eafc m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HAGL. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. Tuy nhi\u00ean Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1062","checkdouble":"190750"},{"date":"11:07 09/07","title":"Davor Suker: \"\u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/davor-suke-noi-ve-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia, Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m, cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 nh\u1edd may m\u1eafn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>R\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3, \u0110T Anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng khi &quot;ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng&quot; thua B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Nh\u1edd v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, Tam S\u01b0 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;d\u1ec5 th\u1edf&quot; h\u01a1n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Davor-Suker-noi-ve-DT-Anh-Ho-da-may-man-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Davor Suker cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m. T\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Davor Suker. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 20 n\u0103m, Croatia m\u1edbi t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, sau th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Davor Suker t\u1ea1i World Cup 1998.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Davor Suker, \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018: &quot;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh vs Colombia t\u1ea1i Moscow, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn. Colombia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean trong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea3 hai?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng Davor Suker cho r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 may r\u1ee7i: &quot;V\u00ec sao c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3? B\u1edfi l\u1ebd c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i th\u00edch. \u0110T Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, 11 \u0111\u1ea5u 11, 11 chi\u1ebfn binh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ti\u1ec1n, xe Ferrari hay \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00fd g\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea3, ch\u1ec9 11 \u0111\u1ea5u 11 \u1edf World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i th\u00edch. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga r\u1ed3i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Croatia v\u00e0 Anh l\u00e0 50 - 50&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-se-het-do-o-ban-ket-vi-chuyen-nay-421-190757.html\">Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft &ldquo;\u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga-421-190734.html\">Kane mu\u1ed1n Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/paul-scholes-pep-co-anh-huong-den-thanh-cong-cua-dt-anh-421-190713.html\">Paul Scholes: Pep c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-tuyen-anh-duoc-khen-het-loi-sau-khi-giup-doi-nha-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-421-190696.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-28-nam-421-190692.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1061","checkdouble":"190752"},{"date":"10:51 09/07","title":"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u00f9ng Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/elneny-hao-huc-truoc-mua-giai-201819-cung-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Elneny t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 khi Arsenal b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.</h2><h2>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo. Anh kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi West Ham h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Elneny \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Pharaoh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m do \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/elneny-hao-huc-truoc-mua-giai-201819-cung-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Emirates, Elneny \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi HLV Wenger ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Elneny v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p Boreham Wood v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5. HLV Unai Emery b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno, trung\u00a0 v\u1ec7 Sokratis, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 3 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn London ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi-172-190748.html\">Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1060","checkdouble":"190754"},{"date":"10:44 09/07","title":"Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft \u201c\u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/anh-se-het-do-o-ban-ket-vi-chuyen-nay.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng to\u00e0n tr\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 nh\u1eb1m ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, Anh vs Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1i t\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p ho\u1eb7c B\u1ec9.</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Croatia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0<br>\r\n</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf theo c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n chia nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u, Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, do s\u1eafc \u00e1o ca-r\u00f4 tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u0169ng tr\u00f9ng m\u00e0u v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Anh, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch xanh t\u00edm than \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trang ph\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trang ph\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Trang-phuc-thi-dau-tran-Anh-vs-Croatia-ban-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Croatia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch m\u00e0u xanh t\u00edm than</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 Croatia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 4 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 x\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc hay sau \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Zlatko Dalic ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u1ed9 c\u00e1nh ca-r\u00f4 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Nigeria, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Argentina (tr\u1eafng xanh) v\u00e0 Iceland (tr\u1eafng) \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 Anh \u2013 ch\u1ec9 m\u1eb7c qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Anh s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1eafc tr\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng sau hai tr\u1eadn knock-out m\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ecf cho d\u1ec5 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u00e1o v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Tam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u00e1o tr\u1eafng khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ea5y, Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft \u201c\u0111\u1ecf\u201d khi kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, trong khi s\u1eafc tr\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u201ckhi\u1ebfn\u201d Tam S\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane nhan doi cach biet tren cham 11 met.\" title=\"Harry Kane nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11 m\u00e9t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/HLV-Wenger-tin-Anh-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-ben-canh-Phap-va-Brazil-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh vs Croatia b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Song song, Croatia c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111ang g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch xanh t\u00edm than c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u1eeb m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng knock-out tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng n\u1ec1 h\u00e0 g\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u201cph\u1ea3i\u201d m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c tranh h\u1ea1ng ba.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190676.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Croatia b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1059","checkdouble":"190757"},{"date":"10:52 09/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 9/7: Di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/ngay-hom-nay-97.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (9/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 Juventus lo ng\u1ea1i, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f2i th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Cristiano Ronaldo. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1eeb si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/ronaldo-den-juventus-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd La Stampa (Italia) cho hay, Real Madrid \u0111\u00f2i th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Juventus. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez th\u1ea5y con s\u1ed1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i 5 th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, khi bi\u1ebft Juventus qu\u00e1 y\u00eau th\u00edch Ronaldo,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, ph\u00eda Real \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 l\u00ean 150 tri\u1ec7u euro, n\u1ebfu Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 7, t\u1ee9c con s\u1ed1 t\u0103ng l\u00ean g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i so v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Real mua Hazard thay Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Neymar, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ee7ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo Marca, nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u201cti\u1ec3u Pele\u201d qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf, Real Madrid chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang s\u0103n Hazard. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a SAO Chelsea t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u01b0a B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u00ednh Brazil c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Courtois khi\u1ebfn Chelsea lo \u00e2u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Mu\u1ed1n g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1, \u201ckho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n 1 tu\u1ea7n sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00ecnh r\u1ed3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d. Hi\u1ec7n anh trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thibaut-courtois-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-172-190602.html\">Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Juventus, PSG, Napoli v\u00e0 Dortmund c\u00f9ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng \u1edf\u00a0 Chelsea, Morata. C\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea-172-190715.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-doi-bong-lon-san-sang-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-bom-xit-chelsea-172-190715.html\">4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alvaro Morata \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Barca mua Willian v\u00e0 Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, sau Paulinho trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi Andre Gomes v\u00e0 Rafinha s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Nou Camp v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, Barca s\u1ebd vung ti\u1ec1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Adrien Rabiot (PSG).</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang-180-190739.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1058","checkdouble":"190759"},{"date":"11:16 09/07","title":"Cha Ozil x\u00fai con trai b\u1ecf tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/cha-ozil-xui-con-trai-bo-tuyen-duc-sau-ky-world-cup-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cha Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng cam l\u00f2ng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn con trai h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00faa r\u00ecu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, qua \u0111\u00f3 khuy\u00ean anh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi\u1ebfn Mannschaft \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m m\u1edbi kh\u1eafc ghi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 huynh khuy\u00ean Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u1ee5 huynh khuy\u00ean Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/cha-ozil-xui-con-trai-bo-tuyen-duc-sau-ky-world-cup-tham-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u1ee5 huynh khuy\u00ean Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#333333\"><br>\r\nPh\u1ee5 huynh khuy\u00ean Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau World Cup 2018</font></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><font color=\"#333333\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, t\u1eeb HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Manuel Neuer, Thomas Muller, Mats Hummels hay Jerome Boateng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mesut Ozil.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Xen gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/duc-chet-di-song-lai-vi-bat-kha-thi-chang-la-cai-tha-gi-het-421-189388.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span> v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn thua Mexico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00e2u ch\u1ec9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, Ozil c\u00f2n d\u00ednh l\u00edu nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00ean l\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, nh\u01b0 c\u00e3i nhau tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi C\u0110V hay ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn con trai h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00faa r\u00ecu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o t\u1ea5m bia \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea1n cho c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, cha Ozil th\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u00f3t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cam t\u00e2m, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn: \u201cN\u1ebfu l\u00e0 n\u00f3 th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i v\u1edbi qu\u00fd v\u1ecb: \u2018C\u1ea3m \u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i.\u2019 N\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nh\u1ea1o b\u00e1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m v\u00e0 ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u1edf s\u00e2n bay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cCon trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i thanh minh cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1ebft khi n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0y nh\u1eefng 9 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eafng l\u00e0 nh\u1edd c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o thua, y nh\u01b0 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Ozil. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho n\u00f3 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb1ng kh\u00e1c!\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-phai-chang-do-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-465-189805.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng do l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga-168-189858.html\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm: B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc-466-189832.html\">Mannschaft b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-phai-chang-tuyen-duc-dang-tro-thanh-nhung-nguoi-anh-moi-421-189831.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-duc-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-2018-cung-su-chuan-bi-toi-te-421-189937.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e2u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1057","checkdouble":"190761"},{"date":"11:04 09/07","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Martinez l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201c\u00f4ng b\u1ee5t\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/quan-diem-bi-va-martinez-la-nhung-ong-but-cua-bong-da.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roberto Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u1eefa t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng l\u00f2ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u00e0 c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (3-2) v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf socola c\u00f3 l\u00fac th\u0103ng, l\u00fac tr\u1ea7m c\u00f9ng th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a World Cup l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft kh\u00e1i qu\u00e1t cho phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p: Th\u00f4ng minh, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh. Cho t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 31, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn Brazil 2-0, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n sau 4 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng b\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng b\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Quan-diem-Martinez-va-DT-Bi-la-nhung-ong-but-cua-bong-da-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Tite, Brazil ch\u1ec9 thua c\u00f3 2 sau 26 tr\u1eadn, 1 trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Selecao ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 8 l\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u00f3, th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Martinez chi\u1ebfm 1/4. N\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i B\u1ec9, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb. HLV Tite c\u1ee7a Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u00edch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190564.html\">HLV Brazil l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n<span>Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9. HLV 57 tu\u1ed5i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Selecao t\u1edbi t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMartinez l\u00e0 &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed1t&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i l\u00ean nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ecd. Roberto Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda m\u00ecnh. L\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i sao nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 44 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a Wigan Athletic v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Everton n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c CLB m\u00e0 Martinez th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh (Wigan v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA r\u1ed3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng). Nh\u01b0ng World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat, n\u01a1i th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u00e1ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Martinez h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0110TQG nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Martinez va Henry\" title=\"HLV Martinez va Henry\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/HLV-Martinez-va-Henry.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean h\u1ebft, Martinez x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1ebfn, th\u00fa v\u1ecb nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ecm trong t\u00ednh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cao \u0111\u1ed9. N\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u00e1u li\u1ec1u&rdquo; v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 su\u1ed1t 2 n\u0103m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft B\u1ec9, Martinez s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil, \u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n sang 4-3-3, g\u00e2y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Nacer Chadli \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Romelu Lukaku ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i Kevin de Bruyne \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn &ldquo;s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Martinez, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Bi du World Cup\" title=\"DT Bi du World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/DT-Bi-du-World-Cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft t\u00e0i n\u0103ng B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u01a1i nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 n\u01a1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n r\u1ee3n ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Martinez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch. Nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho nhau t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Brazil b\u1ecb tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Martinez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed3i sinh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Lukaku t\u1ea1i Everton sau nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y s\u1ed1ng trong ho\u00e0i nghi t\u1ea1i Chelsea. V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n khen ng\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i Man United, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u1ed9 ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil, ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u01a1i tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, anh v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-be-brazil-vao-ban-ket-con-dao-hai-luoi-cua-martinez-421-190620.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/bi-oai-hung-vao-ban-ket-con-dao-hai-luoi-cua-martinez.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-be-brazil-vao-ban-ket-con-dao-hai-luoi-cua-martinez-421-190620.html\">B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Brazil v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft: &ldquo;Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Martinez</span><br>\r\n<span>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil,...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nguy hi\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00ednh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n cao. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n h\u1ecd. Ai bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, HLV Martinez v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi co\u00f3ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa Hazard, De Bruyne v\u00e0 Lukaku ai l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, ai ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, ai &ldquo;s\u1ed1 10&rdquo;, ai &ldquo;s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o&rdquo;&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ghi ban thu 2 cho Bi truoc Brazil\" title=\"De Bruyne ghi ban thu 2 cho Bi truoc Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/HLV-Tite-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Brazil-1-2-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Bruyne b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho t\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kho\u00e9t v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i hay d\u00e2ng cao m\u00e0 Marcelo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Martinez &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111am m\u00ea th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u00e2y th\u01a1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ec9 \u0111ang h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi. X\u00e9t c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hay C\u0110V th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u1ec9. Qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 cho m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft vi\u00ean m\u00e3n!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-roi-world-cup-tite-dang-trach-1-neymar-dang-trach-10-421-190617.html\">Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup: Tite \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 1, Neymar \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch 10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-ha-guc-brazil-hay-cam-on-premier-league-vi-the-he-vang-421-190575.html\">B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Brazil: H\u00e3y c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Premier League v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-brazil-12-bi-noi-dai-con-ac-mong-cua-xu-samba-421-190563.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9: N\u1ed1i d\u00e0i c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 Samba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1056","checkdouble":"190762"},{"date":"07:06 09/07","title":"C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/1/co-mot-doi-bong-dang-lam-moi-cach-de-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau g\u1ea7n 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u0103m 1966, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn, Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y Sir Geoff Hurst, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 1966 l\u00e0m ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0110T Anh l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n&rdquo; &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh\" title=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho nh\u1eefng C\u0110V theo d\u00f5i \u0110T Anh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00fac n\u00e0y, d\u1eabn d\u1eaft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p&rdquo; &ndash; Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, Kane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus 2 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1055","checkdouble":"190731"},{"date":"07:14 09/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (9/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-972018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 9/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></sp