er: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">V\u0110QG TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N 2018 - V\u00d2NG 12</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">10/07 00:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Hammarby - Ostersunds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">V\u0110QG PH\u1ea6N LAN 2018 - V\u00d2NG 19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">09/07 22:30</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Seinajoen JK - RoPS Rovaniemi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">V\u0110QG ICELAND 2018 - V\u00d2NG 12</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">10/07 02:15</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Fylkir - Vikingur Reykjavik</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1054","checkdouble":"190732"},{"date":"07:22 09/07","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. C\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire c\u00f9ng Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 Italia n\u0103m 1990.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111i xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u0103m 1966. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Gareth Southgate cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tri \u00e2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00ec sao \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng k\u1ef3 World Cup tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/HLV-Gareth-Southgate-chia-se-ve-co-hoi-cua-DT-Anh-truoc-ban-ket-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch trong d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. Hi\u1ec7n nay, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111ang b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f2n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi trang ph\u1ee5c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng qu\u1ea7n tr\u1eafng, d\u00f9 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0&rsquo;, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ed9 s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00f9ng m\u00e0u v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o xanh \u0111en.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus 2 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi x\u1ee9 \u0102ng-l\u00ea ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nMang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 - \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay \u0111ang ph\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat-465-190664.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat-465-190664.html\">B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Man Utd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 50 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1053","checkdouble":"190733"},{"date":"07:55 09/07","title":"Kane mu\u1ed1n Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau g\u1ea7n 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u0103m 1966, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn, Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y Sir Geoff Hurst, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 1966 l\u00e0m ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0110T Anh l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1966, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n&rdquo; &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh\" title=\"Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho nh\u1eefng C\u0110V theo d\u00f5i \u0110T Anh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00fac n\u00e0y, d\u1eabn d\u1eaft to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng ai mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p&rdquo; &ndash; Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, Kane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus 2 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1052","checkdouble":"190734"},{"date":"08:09 09/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.\r\n</h2><h2>Croatia t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi Moscow tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-ro s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua d\u00e0n s\u01b0 t\u1eed tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Croatia ph\u1ea3i ng\u0103n kh\u00f4ng cho \u0110T Anh ghi b\u00e0n, hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng Leo Messi, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia &ndash; Zlatko Dalic tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kane v\u00e0 Sterling l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn\" title=\"HLV Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-len-tieng-thach-thuc-anh-o-ban-ket.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 \u0110T Anh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Harry Kane l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n anh \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen, v\u00ec v\u1eady hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kane.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0o d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng pha d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to c\u1ee7a Anh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Raheen Sterling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Harry Kane. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ecd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190676.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190676.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Croatia b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nLuka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190675.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga-421-190675.html\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nga</span><br>\r\nZlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1051","checkdouble":"190735"}]}